```

2. Connect phone with ADB:

```powershell
& "C:\Program Files (x86)\Android\android-sdk\platform-tools\adb.exe" connect PHONE_IP:PORT
```

3. Verify phone is connected:

```powershell
& "C:\Program Files (x86)\Android\android-sdk\platform-tools\adb.exe" devices -l
```

4. Set reverse tunnel:

```powershell
& "C:\Program Files (x86)\Android\android-sdk\platform-tools\adb.exe" reverse tcp:5117 tcp:5117
```

5. Verify reverse exists:

```powershell
& "C:\Program Files (x86)\Android\android-sdk\platform-tools\adb.exe" reverse --list
```

You should see:

```text
